result.name: Fu Doo Restaurant

reviews.text: I ordered a fried rice and a lemon honey. The waitress jotted down the price on a slip as usual as other this type HK style fast-food restaurants. After a while, another waitress came and looked at the slip with a disgusted face. Then she said very impolite like I getting a fault, "The price is not this. It's not   set price. And, cold drink, you drink cold drink, and with honey Bahbahbahbah bah...." I couldn't help her attitude anymore. I stopped her nagging complaint. And said, "Can you stop your blaming? I am the customer, not your subordinate! Written down a wrong price that's not my responsibility. How much a fried rice with a drink only? You correct well the price and leave please ! " She stopped her mouth with a face she feeling disgusted still and flied the correct slip on my table. I had a look the slip. Eleven dollars added for a lemon honey, total price $69. And I didn't know still why I was blamed by her.
Good food at good price. They also dont rush you.
No matter of quick lunch sets or fancy dinner dishes, I ever had much wonderful hours here .
Good place.
Convenient

result.name: 富都茶餐廳

reviews.text: 好
食物質素一般…環境更一般！如非特别情况。不考慮再去！
地方污漕地上油笠笠好易跣親，坐位污漬斑斑，枱面沒有清潔，食物質素像一般的茶餐廰的難食，不去也巴！
Ok 啲嘢都幾好食但係個冷氣好凍 冷氣唔知點解呢成日都漏水
正宗 港式茶 餐 廳， 所有大路港式粥粉麵飯菜式都有 ， 沒有意外驚喜 ，主要亮點是24小時營業，是荃灣市中心凌晨後，主要的平民食肆。
